data.description: BIG PRICE DROP and NEW CARPET IN THE BEDROOMS!  Charming as all get-out and now it smells like a new home!  This sprawling, open floorplan is sure to please your buyers looking for both comfort and flair.  Soaring ceilings cover the expansive area that contains the living room with corner fireplace, generous dining area, and the island kitchen with loads of counter space, beautiful detail in the cabinet work, stainless appliances, granite tops, accent lighting, and a walk-in pantry.  Four bedrooms set in a split plan offer plenty of room for activities and privacy to boot.  The oversized rear covered patio leads into a very usable back yard that is fenced and irrigated.  Guest bath, stylish color selections, elegant lighting, and a massive garden tub and separate shower in the master are just a few more of the bountiful amenities you'll find when you tour this treasure.  Call today and see it today.
